raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Waaa what a tiring day
Mabel: I just feel like...
Mabel: sfx: bedcreak2: *creak*
Mabel: Collapsing on my bed 🫠
Mabel: PinkThought: I couldn't do it yesterday, maybe today?
Mabel: PinkThought: Here goes..
Mabel: img: mabel/77
Mabel: 😊
- Wow, so pretty
	Player: Wow, so pretty!
	Mabel: Thanks!
	Mabel: Thought: I gotta mention it better next time
- Welcome back!
	Player: Welcome back!
	Mabel: Thanks babe 🥰
	Mabel: Thought: OMG he didn't even notice
	Mabel: Thought: I have to take a better one next time
Mabel: How was your day? 😁..
Mabel: Did you eat healthy??
Player: It was okay
Player: I ate my sandwich!
Mabel: That's good 😊
Mabel: Be healthy cause we have a long life to live together 🥰
Mabel: Oh I wanted to ask you
Mabel: Did you want to maybe go on a date on Sunday?
if Story.pink_heart == 0:
	Mabel: I know you've been busy but
	Mabel: I really want to see you this time
- I can [#pinkheart]
	set Story.pink_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Date3\"
	Player: I can!
	Mabel: 🥹
	Mabel: That makes me so happy
	Mabel: We'll figure something really fun out for the weekend!
	Player: Can't wait!
- I can't with work going on [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Week3Work\") == true]
	Player: I can't with work going on babe
	if Story.pink_heart == 0:
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 15
		Mabel: Thought: Are we ever going to go on a date...?
		Mabel: Thought: I miss being with you
	Player: Sorry
	Mabel: It's okay!
- I can't with work going on [#dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Week3Work\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Week3Work\"
	Player: I can't with work going on babe
	if Story.pink_heart == 0:
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 15
		Mabel: Thought: Are we ever going to go on a date...?
		Mabel: Thought: I miss being with you
	Player: Sorry
	Mabel: It's okay!
Player: Have you picked a club yet?
Mabel: Ohh!!
Mabel: The clubs! 
Mabel: Almost forgot about that
Mabel: There's been so much talk about it
Mabel: All the huge signs and posters everywhere..
Mabel: It's seriously a bigger thing than I thought lol
Player: Yeah it seems like it
Mabel: Naomi and Nina have been both asking me to join all week 😵‍💫
Mabel: Some other clubs were stopping me in the hallways too begging me 🥹
Mabel: I felt so bad when I told them no 😭
Player: So undecided still?
Mabel: Actually...
Mabel: I did decide!
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	set Story.flag = \"NTR\"
	Mabel: I thought the Sorority club is quite popular but not many girls get in
	if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
		set Story.flag = \"LUST\"
		Mabel: And looks like the girls there have a lot of status or something lol 🤔
	else:
		set Story.flag = \"LOVE\"
		Mabel: And looks like the girls there have a lot of status or something lol 🤔
	Mabel: The grant and benefits are really good!
	Mabel: I'm not sure about all the details of what they do but Nina says it'll be a lot of fun 😇
	Mabel: So I can't wait!!
	Player: Nice, sounds great!
	Mabel: Thanks! 🥰
	Mabel: I'm gonna fill in my sign up sheet tomorrow and apply on Friday!
	Mabel: Apparently I'm a lucky one to get in 🤭
	Mabel: But I was hoping we could be in the same club but Sorority thing is only for girls 🥺
	Mabel: Are you going to join a club?
	Player: Hmm, I haven't had the same luck
	Player: I'll have to find one soon I guess
	Mabel: What about that friend of yours?
	Player: Oh right, maybe I'll ask
	Mabel: You could also have no club I guess but that's up to you
	Mabel: Curious to see what you might join 😁
	Mabel: But I'll tell you all about our girls club when I can!
	Player: For sure
	Mabel: Can't wait to know what you join hehe
	Mabel: I gotta go and start my assignment
	Mabel: I just wanna nap like a big ol' lazy cat though 😩
	Player: Get your work done!
	Mabel: Jeez fine, ttyl 😘
	Player: Bye!
else:
	set Story.flag = \"NTS\"
	Mabel: I want to help Naomi with the Photography Club!
	if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
		set Story.flag = \"LUST\"
	else:
		set Story.flag = \"LOVE\"
	Mabel: She and Ms Suzanna are so nice to me so I thought I'd join
	Mabel: I feel like it'll be a lot of fun
	Mabel: Plus you can join too! 
	Mabel: Since the Sorority is a girls only club
	Mabel: We can be together 😇
	Mabel: Would you like that?
	Player: I would!
	Mabel: Really? 😍
	Mabel: Omg that's so exciting 😊
	Player: How do I join?
	Mabel: I'll tell Naomi you want to join
	Mabel: I'm sure she'll be happy to hear it!
	Mabel: She can send you an application!
	Player: Sounds good!
	Mabel: Alright I'll go do that now!
	Mabel: TTYL
	Player: Thanks babe
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
